Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7. Your main focus should always be your customers. 8. Staying in business requires adapting to change constantly.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 9. If you don't invest in yourself, don't expect others to. 10. Your first business should have a low upfront cost and provide you with good cash flow'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 11. If you don't work for the life you want, you're gonna have to settle Ûor the one you currently have. 12. Your ability to solve problems directly impacts your income.'.

node.text:
Are you ready to become harder to kill? Then keep reading!

The number one way to get ahead in life is to learn a new skill. The more skills you obtain, the more successful you will be, the more successful you are, the harder you are to kill.

Did you know that on average it only takes about 6 months to obtain a new skill that could change your life forever?

So then why is it that most people never learn new skills or educate themselves?

The answer is simple. They lack the discipline. They'd rather stay comfortable and spend their spare time relaxing instead of using it to DISAPPEAR to learn and improve.

But not you, you're different. You recognize the value of your time and are hungry to improve.

By chasing success and improvement, you will live a more purposeful and meaningful life, a life that others only dream of.

For that reason, I personally recommend you follow some of the best mentors on Instagram, their regular posts and updates will enhance your skills and give you the mindset necessary to be impossible to kill!

Their pages are as follows:

1. @valenmatvei

2. @alexpxladi

3. @financethinks

4. @moneydesires

5. @stefstundner

6. @wealthconduct
